3. Write a query to get the distinct Mondays from hiredate in emp tables.

SQL> select hiredate, next_day(hiredate-1,'Monday') as next_monday from emp where next_day(hiredate-1, 'Monday')=hiredate;

HIREDATE  NEXT_MOND
--------- ---------
28-SEP-81 28-SEP-81


